name: Astronaut In The Ocean (luissart96)
description:
This is a wonderful game where you have to go for the precious stone at the end of the road, but first, you need to beat all the enemies, be careful, some of them have a few surprises...

Main changes:

1) UI rearranged, with new buttons and style.

2) Invisible enemy added, be careful, it can be a real problem...

3) Jumping enemy added, you would not even see it coming.

4) Level 2 with a significant way to go.

Please enjoy and have fun!
